+{"id":"bd-1sx","title":"Add version/output_format envelope fields to robot-forecast, robot-capacity, robot-burndown","description":"Legacy Go output includes 'version' and 'output_format' fields in robot-forecast, robot-capacity, and robot-burndown output envelopes. Rust implementation omits these. Add them for full field parity.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-27T19:03:01.814656291Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-27T19:10:26.773950611Z","closed_at":"2026-02-27T19:10:26.773932828Z","close_reason":"Added output_format and version envelope fields to RobotForecastOutput and RobotCapacityOutput, matching Go legacy. Conformance assertions verify output_format='json' and version starts with 'v'. All tests pass.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
