+{"id":"bd-2i6","title":"Conformance: large-dataset stress-test fixtures and adversarial edge cases","description":"Background: large/adversarial fixture coverage is a critical parity confidence lever and already partially underway.\\nWork: expand and harden stress fixtures (size, shape, pathological dependencies, malformed metadata) and keep fixture intent documented.\\nAcceptance: fixture suite reproduces known edge conditions and catches regression classes that minimal fixtures miss.\\nTesting/logging: fixture generation and validation steps must emit detailed metadata and provenance logs.","status":"in_progress","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-27T21:53:17.916549894Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-05T04:11:10.414331844Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2i6","depends_on_id":"bd-33w.6","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-05T04:19:07Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-2i6","depends_on_id":"bd-33w.6.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-05T04:19:07Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
